text: Nadzeya Makarchanka (born 1998) is a Belarusian sprint canoeist. She participated at the 2018 ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships, winning a medal.C-2 500 m results ==References== Category:Living people Category:1998 births Category:Belarusian female canoeists Category:ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships medalists in Canadian Category:European Games competitors for Belarus Category:Canoeists at the 2019 European Games Category:European Games medalists in canoeing Category:European Games silver medalists for Belarus
